  "description": "Curated tetrapod sperm protamine-1 (PRM1 / galline) dataset for comparative biophysics. Sequences retrieved from UniProt (June 2026). 'system' classifies the chromatin-stabilization strategy: 'disulfide' (cysteine-rich, eutherian-type) vs 'electrostatic' (cysteine-poor, arginine-hyperenriched). [v2: expanded to 46 taxa per 2026-07-18 pre-registration — +21 taxa: 4 cysteine-bearing Planigale (independent origin), 6 cysteine-free dasyurid sisters, 10 family-breadth marsupials, Alligator.]",
